LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
getScriptVersion(specifier) {
  debug(`host.getScriptVersion("${specifier}")`);
  const sourceFile = sourceFileCache.get(specifier);
  if (sourceFile) {
    return sourceFile.version ?? "1";
  }
  return core.jsonOpSync("op_script_version", { specifier });
}
```

